column2: Middleware with case-sensitive paths do not protect endpoints with case-insensitive paths.
column4: This route uses a case-sensitive path [["pattern"|"relative:///VulnFinder-CodeQL-main/src/javascript-cwe/CWE-178/examples/CaseSensitiveMiddlewarePath.js:3:9:3:21"]], but is guarding a [["case-insensitive path"|"relative:///VulnFinder-CodeQL-main/src/javascript-cwe/CWE-178/examples/CaseSensitiveMiddlewarePath.js:11:1:13:2"]]. A path such as '/ADMIN/USERS/1' will bypass the middleware.
